## You are an ideal candidate for an accountant position if you:
* Advanced in PCs, Google Sheets, and Excel.
* Have teamwork skills.
* Your English is at B1 level and above.
## Responsibilities of an accountant include:
* payroll accounting on a monthly basis;
* accounting of customer payments;
* correspondence with customers regarding payments and profits for employees;
* sending contracts and other forms to new employees for filling;
* accounting of the company’s current expenses;
* accounting of days off and vacations of employees;
* tracking and accounting payments of our debtors;
* solving other current problems and issues.
It will be an advantage if you have experience of working with contracts and accounting source documents or have had economic education. But if not, don’t worry – we’re ready to teach you.
Record a[video interview](/videointerview) in English and we will contact you as soon as possible.
